ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectDESIGNATED BARLEY - 2008-2009 Fixing Final Payment amount **
PrecisApproval of the amount determined by THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD for each tonne of each grade of DESIGNATED BARLEY to be distributed by THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to the producers for the pool period that began on August 1, 2008 and ended on July 31, 2009.
